{"data":[{"date":"09:51 31/07","title":"Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/chiellini-noi-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chiellini n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y t\u1eebng nghi ng\u1edd t\u00ednh kh\u1ea3 thi khi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f9ng Juventus sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau khi c\u00f9ng Real v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i. R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 n\u00edu k\u00e9o t\u1eeb l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Los Blancos, CR7 v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chiellini n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chiellini n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/chiellini-noi-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chiellini n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Giorgio Chiellini n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 13 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bianconeri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eebng nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng ngay t\u1eeb khi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nghe th\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus, t\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng: Kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o!\u201d, t\u1edd ESPN tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Chiellini. \u201cSau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u1ea3 thi. V\u1edbi HLV, v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJuventus \u0111ang \u0111i l\u00ean n\u0103m n\u00e0y qua n\u0103m kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng anh \u1ea5y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-dau-quan-cho-juve-dieu-gi-dung-dang-sau-thuong-vu-bac-ty-187-190988.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/del-pierro-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-dau-quan-cho-juve-dieu-gi-dung-dang-sau-thuong-vu-bac-ty-187-190988.html\">Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juve: \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c t\u1ef7?</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n Ronaldo chia tay Real \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u00f9 m\u00f9 v\u1ec1 Bonucci</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n cho l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Joao Cancelo, Mattia Perin v\u00e0 Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus. T\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Bianconeri s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua l\u1ea1i Leonardo Bonucci t\u1eeb AC Milan ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Chiellini \u2013 b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Bonucci b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Bonucci l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t\u201d, Chiellini n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Bonucci v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch hay t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 xem Bonucci c\u00f3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai-176-192360.html\">S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo-176-192279.html\">R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4874","checkdouble":"192376"},{"date":"09:19 31/07","title":"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. Theo \u0111\u00f3, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao mang n\u1eeda d\u00f2ng m\u00e1u Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-khong-nghi-toi-chuyen-thang-thua-khi-len-tuyen.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf FLC Thanh Ho\u00e1.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;, \u00f4ng Park n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC, HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1eb7n k\u1ebd: &quot;\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef t\u1ed1t phong \u0111\u1ed9. Ch\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp, c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Trong ba th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd cho t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 7 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc khi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam bao g\u1ed3m Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Ng\u1ecdc Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1u \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i V-League. HLV Park Hang-seo cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m PVF trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 31/7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 c\u00fap Vinaphone di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8/2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi-168-192323.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dinh-trong-tro-lai-hlv-park-hang-seo-cam-cua-bao-chi-168-192323.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda&rsquo; b\u00e1o ch\u00ed</span><br />\r\nBu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng 30/7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng dai d\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-cho-hong-duy-lo-tieu-chi-chon-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-192311.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc cho H\u1ed3ng Duy, l\u1ed9 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4873","checkdouble":"192379"},{"date":"10:24 31/07","title":"HLV HAGL tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-tin-tuong-hoc-tro-se-tao-nen-su-khac-biet-tai-olympic-viet-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV HAGL \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL tin h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, \u0111a s\u1ed1 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, cho n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00f4i, \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i U23, c\u00e1c HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 HAGL n\u00f3i ri\u00eang. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD 18. Suy cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t\u201d, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o Bongdaplus.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo ng\u1ea1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t sau khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i V-League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo l\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u0169ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, V-League ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trung b\u00ecnh 1 tu\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 2 tr\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i V-League, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duoc-thay-park-ngoi-khen-thu-mon-dang-van-lam-sang-cua-bat-chinh-168-192379.html\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park ng\u1ee3i khen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4872","checkdouble":"192384"},{"date":"10:48 31/07","title":"Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vtv-co-mua-ban-quyen-aff-cup-2018-0133c047.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup 2018 qu\u00e1 cao khi\u1ebfn VTV ch\u00f9n b\u01b0\u1edbc</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang t\u0103ng phi m\u00e3, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang t\u0103ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 EURO, World Cup m\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c, ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u0169ng h\u00f2a chung xu th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD, \u0111ang r\u1ed9 l\u00ean tin \u0111\u1ed3n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n qu\u00e1 cao. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh AFF Cup 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u00ec n\u0103m 2016. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018, VTV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 tri\u1ec7u USD. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 phi l\u00fd cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 khu v\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu VTV kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4871","checkdouble":"192386"},{"date":"09:40 31/07","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-golovin-toi-monaco.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Michael Emenalo&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMichael Emenalo, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monaco hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Aleksandr Golovin t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-khi-Golovin-toi-Monaco-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Michael Emenalo gi\u00fap Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Emenalo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1edbi Monaco, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Michael Emenalo khi\u1ebfn Golovin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, song \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Monaco ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Marina Granovskaia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marina Granovskaia l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n b\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Granovskaia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marina Granovskaia dang khong lam tot cong viec cua minh\" title=\"Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marina Granovskaia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m Golovin tr\u01b0\u1edbc Monaco, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Marina Granovskaia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea m\u1edbi chi ra 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m Jorginho v\u00e0 Robert Green. T\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani, Pjanic v\u00e0 Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Marina Granovskaia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Jorginho v\u00e0 Kante l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co co hoi da chinh khi Chelsea khong chieu mo thanh cong Golovin\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/bas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Golovin \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRuben Loftus-Cheek v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Barkley c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Maurizio Sarri&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea ph\u1ea3i mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga. Song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc BL\u0110 The Blues \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri da khong the co duoc Golovin trong doi hinh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 38 tu\u1ed5i Robert Green.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Hazard, Willian hay Morata, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Rugani hay Higuain \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Sarri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 m\u00e1y Chelsea tr\u01a1n tru \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Nga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bong da Nga huong loi khi Golovin toi Monaco\" title=\"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea, Golovin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGolovin t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t may \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/chinh-thuc-monaco-chieu-mo-aleksandr-golovin-197-192165.html\" target=\"_blank\">Golovin \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco</span> thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Jardim r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo Jardim&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leonardo Jardim \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u00d4ng bi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, Monaco t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leonardo Jardim lai co mot cau thu tiem nang de nhao nhan thanh sao lon\" title=\"Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0o nh\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh sao l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u01a1n 400 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Kylian Mbappe, Fabinho, Thomas Lemar, Benjamin Mendy, Bernardo Silva v\u00e0 Tiemoue Bakayoko.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Golovin h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Leonardo Jardim l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n Monaco ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Golovin trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4870","checkdouble":"192381"},{"date":"10:49 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-tottenham-vs-ac-milan-07h30-ngay-18-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham vs AC Milan l\u00fac 07h30 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham vs AC Milan 07h30 ng\u00e0y 18 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/01-08-18-icc-2018-nhan-dinh-bong-da-cua-cac-chuyen-gia-nha-cai-bet98vn-tottenham-vs-ac-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham vs AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Tottenham vs AC Milan: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau World Cup d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barcelona c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai ng\u00e0y (2-2). Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho N\u2019Koudou s\u00fat b\u1ed3i ghi b\u00e0n.\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Son, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft Eriksen c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Roma v\u00e0 Barcelona. Nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Son v\u00e0 Eriksen, Tottenham v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Carter-Vickers, Walker-Peters c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ecd x\u00e1t v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPochettino c\u00f2n t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u1eebng tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 33 tu\u1ed5i Fernando Llorente ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Roma. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Lucas Moura, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Roma. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 PSG b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t v\u0169 kh\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Harry Kane ch\u01b0a h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Milan v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai, nh\u1eefng Llorente, Son, Lamela s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pochettino. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u00ec tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Spurs kh\u00e1 mong manh do Pochettino \u0111ang th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Milan s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Spurs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Tottenham, Milan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1eeb lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8. \u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Man Utd, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Gattuso b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gattuso c\u0169ng \u0111ang lung lay t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng khi Milan chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng quan m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t \u0111ang nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Tottenham. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Spurs s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Son, Eriksen, Lucas Moura. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Tottenham thua 9, th\u1eafng 1/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Milan th\u1eafng 7, thua 3/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Tottenham th\u1eafng 4, thua 6/10 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Milan th\u1eafng 7, thua 3/10 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Tottenham th\u1eafng 2, thua 1/3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Milan theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u1edbi 13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Tottenham k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong 4/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Milan. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy lu\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4869","checkdouble":"192387"},{"date":"09:18 31/07","title":"Sao Roma cay c\u00fa s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/manolas-phat-bieu-ve-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manolas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Malcom v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00e0ng quan. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a Barcelona c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 g\u00ec.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Manolas kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Malcom l\u00e0 ai</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAS Roma \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Malcom c\u1ee7a Bordeaux. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, sao tr\u1ebb Brazil v\u00e0 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;l\u1eadt k\u00e8o&rdquo; ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n, tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n, Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Malcom v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ph\u00eda Roma kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 vui v\u1ebb. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m l\u1edbn chuy\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 Bordeaux v\u00e0 Barca ra t\u00f2a \u00e1n th\u1ec3 thao qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Manolas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Malcom v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00e0ng quan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Manolas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Malcom v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00e0ng quan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/manolas-phat-bieu-ve-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Manolas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Malcom v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh c\u1edd khi v\u00e0o 9h05 s\u00e1ng mai (1/8), Malcom s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Barca \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Roma \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i, trung v\u1ec7 Kostas Manolas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Malcom v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cay nghi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Malcom l\u00e0 ai, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quen h\u1eafn ta&rdquo;, Manolas n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u1edf Dallas khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 Malcom. &ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barcelona, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1eafn ta c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o. H\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Roma th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn sang Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: &ldquo;Mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n<span>Cay c\u00fa xen l\u1eabn h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 cho n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t Malcom. Theo \u0111\u00f3, AS Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Barca nh\u1ea3 Messi cho h\u1ecd.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nB\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKostas Manolas chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Roma t\u1eeb Olympiacos m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u Euro. 4 n\u0103m qua, trung v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Giallorossi. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Manolas kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Roma d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft Chelsea, Man United, PSG r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh Barca li\u00ean h\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i&rdquo;, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 xinh \u0111\u1eb9p. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi xa n\u01a1i n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Roma tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-hoi-mua-nzonzi-172-192318.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-chuan-bi-khoi-kien-bordeaux-vi-lat-keo-vu-malcom-184-191956.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux v\u00ec l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen-176-191948.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-hang-hot-bailey-172-192291.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4868","checkdouble":"192375"},{"date":"09:17 31/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cao nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00ec sao Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Vi-sao-Real-Madrid-mua-Thibaut-Courtois-van-chua-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Thibaut Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. Real \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n nh\u1eb1m nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Los Blancos v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real Madrid mua Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay&nbsp;th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Chelsea-se-mua-Jordan-Pickford-thay-Courtois-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Courtois n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111ang nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a Leicester, Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton...</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 nh\u1eafm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Courtois kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Khi \u0111\u00f3 Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 H\u00e8 2019 \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4867","checkdouble":"192377"},{"date":"11:14 31/07","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Simeone n\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang, Ronaldo gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n Messi!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/quan-diem-simeone-noi-dung-ronaldo-gia-tri-hon-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u00d4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn CR7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f2n Leo th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Simeone l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi, ai h\u01a1n ai l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 n\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch say m\u00ea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft ch\u00e1n. Sau c\u00f9ng, <em>Ronaldo c\u00f3 hay h\u01a1n Messi hay kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng li\u00ean k\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/iniesta-chia-tay-barca-messi-con-no-anh-2-qua-bong-vang-180-186764.html\">Iniesta chia tay Barca: Messi c\u00f2n n\u1ee3 anh 2 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi-184-183504.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ronaldo h\u00f3a &ldquo;Th\u00e1nh&rdquo;, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2017-khong-chi-ngang-messi-180-174863.html\">Ronaldo gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2017: S\u00e1nh ngang Messi? \u1ed2 kh\u00f4ng&hellip;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng <strong>nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi</strong>. M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang v\u00e0 t\u1ef1u chung h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <u>d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 Simeone, \u00f4ng th\u00edch Ronaldo h\u01a1n</u>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Ronaldo-va-Messi-qua-nx-Simeone.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Simeone, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u1ec9 1 trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i oan gia Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid. V\u1edbi <strong>Messi, anh ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i hay khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh</strong> v\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y th\u1eed \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ecba v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Simeone, ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1c. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 Barca. <em>\u0110\u1eb7t Messi sang b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c</em> ngo\u00e0i g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia, <em>anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m v\u00e0 Ronaldo th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon-180-192278.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/giua-messi-va-ronaldo-simeone-chon-ai-xuat-sac-hon-180-192278.html\">Gi\u1eefa Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo, Simeone ch\u1ecdn ai xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n?</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u00d4ng cho r\u1eb1ng trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao, Lionel Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nRonaldo gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, <u>Messi \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i theo \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111en</u>. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng tr\u1eddi ph\u00fa cho nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai mu\u1ed1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3. Ronaldo c\u00f3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao l\u1edbn l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Messi. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111i nh\u01b0 bay m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n n\u1ed5i. Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn <em>ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n</em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Messi\" title=\"Ronaldo va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Ronaldo-va-Messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Simeone tin Ronaldo to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n Messi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Argentina, Simeone c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt: <strong>Messi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3</strong>. M\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u00ec l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao n\u1eb7ng t\u00ednh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i tennis, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Roger Federer hay Rafael Nadal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, <u>Messi kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</u>. M\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng \u0110T Argentina v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Leo c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu. \u0110\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango c\u0169ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd xem Messi \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Diego Maradona, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a Argentina t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi that vong Argentina\" title=\"Messi that vong Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Messi-that-vong-Argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Leo n\u1ee3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi \u0111\u1ea1t 9, 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi ch\u01a1i cho Barcelona th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6, 7 khi l\u00ean Argentina. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a anh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Tango nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua lu\u00f4n n\u1edf r\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c Mauro Icardi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, Paulo Dybala ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Argentina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m \u1edf anh</strong>. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch gom to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00ean s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng Leo \u1edf \u0110TQG, m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon-421-189520.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon-421-189520.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n?</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u00e0 c\u1eb7p k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong 10 n\u0103m qua, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa 2 si\u00eau nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou, Messi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 su\u1ed1t 17 n\u0103m qua. T\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi 14 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra Messi, \u0111\u01b0a anh t\u1eeb Argentina t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o. Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat xa l\u1ea1 n\u00e0o v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca khi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 b\u1edfi h\u1ed3n c\u1ed1t Tiki-Taka xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, khi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1, <u>Messi c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</u>. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t, anh ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Ronaldinho, Thierry Henry, Samuel Eto'o, Xavi, Andres Iniesta, David Villa, Zlatan Ibrahimovic, Neymar v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Luis Suarez, Phil Coutinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du Messi chi vao san tu bang ghe du bi\" title=\"D\u00f9 Messi ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/18/tong-hop-celta-vigo-22-barca-vong-33-la-liga-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 &quot;\u00f4ng vua con&quot; t\u1ea1i Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho Messi</u>. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u00e9p ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00e1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00e2n s\u1ee7ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Barca d\u00e0nh cho Messi. \u1ede m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Messi c\u00f3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</strong> nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Andorinha v\u00e0 Nacional t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 kinh qua 3 CLB bao g\u1ed3m Sporting Lisbon (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha), Man United (Anh), Real Madrid (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>T\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t</em>. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ecdi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Cristiano-Ronaldo-Co-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo d\u00e1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f2n Messi th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t gi\u1ea3 thi\u1ebft Simeone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn s\u1edf h\u1eefu ho\u1eb7c Ronaldo ho\u1eb7c Messi cho Atletico Madrid. Tin ch\u1eafc, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 qu\u00fd m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn Messi cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao cao 1m70 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Inter Milan n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Barca, song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf l\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi k\u00fd cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <u>tr\u1ecdn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Messi s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou</u>. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y anh ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf m\u1edbi n\u00f3i <em>Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n Ronaldo th\u00ec c\u00f3</em>. \u0110\u1ebfn Argentina v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, Leo c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c c\u01a1 m\u00e0&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/neymar-va\u0300-messi-hit-khoi-ronaldo-ve-thu-nhap-tren-instagram-188-192144.html\">Neymar va\u0300 Messi 'h\u00edt kh\u00f3i' Ronaldo v\u1ec1 thu nh\u1eadp tr\u00ean Instagram</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cassano-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-messi-180-191515.html\">N\u1ebfu Ronaldo l\u00e0 Nadal, Messi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Federer</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec&hellip; Messi?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4866","checkdouble":"192389"},{"date":"09:51 31/07","title":"Man City th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/man-city-tho-phao-voi-chan-thuong-cua-bom-tan-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cho tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs Man City tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chia tay Leicester City \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB</span>, Riyad Mahrez h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t n\u00e0o trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/man-city-tho-phao-voi-chan-thuong-cua-bom-tan-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ef1c ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00e3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria c\u00f2n d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City 3-2 Bayern Munich \u1edf IC Cup 2018. Theo ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, anh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 Man City theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i tinh vui \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady N\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Riyad Mahrez kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1eaft c\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i g\u00ec v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh g\u1eb7p Chelsea cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa hai nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Wembley, n\u01a1i Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t &ldquo;t\u00e2n binh&rdquo; Maurizio Sarri b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-tiet-lo-ve-chan-thuong-mahrez-172-192249.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/guardiola-tiet-lo-ve-chan-thuong-mahrez.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-tiet-lo-ve-chan-thuong-mahrez-172-192249.html\">Guardiola lo l\u1eafng cho ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Man City</span><br>\r\nGuardiola ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Mahrez. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111au m\u1eaft c\u00e1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern Munich v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1eb7ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4865","checkdouble":"192378"},{"date":"10:10 31/07","title":"\"T\u00e2n binh\" Man Utd tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Mourinho x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Man Utd \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Andreas Pereira c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n \u1edf Valencia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Andreas Pereira n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pereira c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00ecnh, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua \u1edf Valencia v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00fd b\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nhanh v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n h\u01a1n, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1m ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i l\u1ea7m c\u0169 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ed1n d\u0129 mang s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 10 ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, gi\u1edd Pereira \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 chia b\u00e0i, m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hoan ngh\u00eanh vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i n\u00f3i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1. HLV h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf t\u00f4i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Michael Carrick \u0111\u1ec1u s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean t\u00f4i trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, gi\u00fap t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi ra th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u hay l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-truoc-mua-giai-201819-va-nu-cuoi-mim-cua-mourinho-172-192083.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec9m c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span><br>\r\nG\u1ea1t lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m v\u1edbi Milan sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Tuy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-truoc-mua-giai-chet-boi-cam-bay-cua-chinh-minh-172-192305.html\">Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Ch\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea1m b\u1eaby c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i, Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00fac quen thu\u1ed9c xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi Man Utd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb bao ph\u1ee7 b\u1edfi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4864","checkdouble":"192380"},{"date":"10:13 31/07","title":"HLV Leicester n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Claude Puel t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng Leicester c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Harry Maguire tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 t\u1eeb Man United.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Maguire \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, Man \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi mang v\u1ec1 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Lee Grant. M\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho.</div>\r\n<h2>Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Puel\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Leicester n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Leicester n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv-leicester-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-mu-chieu-mo-maguire.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Puel ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Claude Puel \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Maguire gia nh\u1eadp Man United trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Maguire m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Maguire v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Vardy. H\u1ecd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4863","checkdouble":"192382"},{"date":"10:42 31/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri gay g\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Gary Neville quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 y\u00ean khi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1eb7c m\u00f9i ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0n em.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng r\u1ebb nh\u01b0 cho so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c Xherdan Shaqiri t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n sau khi Stoke City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Premier League.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ee9t \u00e1o ra \u0111i v\u00ec s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaqiri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh v\u1eabn b\u1ecb <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-buong-loi-dap-tra-khi-bi-huyen-thoai-mu-chui-thang-mat-172-192056.html\" target=\"_blank\">anh em nh\u00e0 Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng to\u00e0n t\u00e2m to\u00e0n \u00fd cho Stoke, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i cho d\u1ec5 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man Utd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1edbi m\u00f3c v\u1edb v\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cd\u00ecm h\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 IC Cup 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Man Utd \u0111\u1ebfn 4-1, v\u1edbi Shaqiri ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00fa xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Gary Neville c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed3m mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em thua k\u00e9m g\u1ea7n 20 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Shaqiri ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n Ronaldinho th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 hay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebfng, ch\u1ec9 th\u00edch \u0111\u1ee9ng y\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u00edch Shaqiri, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Xin ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu ta ra sao v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-172-192043.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4862","checkdouble":"192383"}]}